### <a id='advanced-mode-banner'></a> Advanced Mode UI Banner

Ops Manager displays a banner when you are in Advanced Mode. This helps you understand when you are in Advanced Mode. It also helps ensure that you remember to exit Advanced Mode when you complete the required work. 

For more information about how to enable Advanced Mode in Ops Manager, see the [Unlockable Fields](https://docs.pivotal.io/platform/2-9/customizing/lock-on-deploy.html#unlock) section in _Ops Manager Fields That Lock On Deploy_.


